{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"029172bccc","title":"对柯庆施同志有关上海曲艺革命化改革总结报告的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b0a2557de2","index":0,"year":1963,"month":12,"day":12,"articleId":"029172bccc","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6c95d13523","type":"title","text":"对柯庆施同志有关上海曲艺革命化改革总结报告的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"029172bccc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"15da507c5b","type":"paragraph","text":"此件可以一看。各种艺术形式――戏剧、曲艺、音乐、美术、舞蹈、电影、诗和文学等等，问题不少，人数很多，社会主义改造在许多部门中，至今收效甚微。许多部门至今还是“死人”统治着。不能低估电影、新诗、民歌、美术、小说的成绩，但其中的问题也不少。至于戏剧等部门，问题就更大了。社会经济基础已经改变了，为这个基础服务的上层建筑之一的艺术部门，至今还是大问题。这需要从调查研究着手，认真地抓起来。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"029172bccc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6aec239400","type":"paragraph","text":"许多共产党人热心提倡封建主义和资本主义的艺术，却不热心提倡社会主义的艺术，岂非咄咄怪事。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"029172bccc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b39e6a4a8f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"029172bccc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"23e114b526","type":"subdate","text":"一九六三年十二月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"029172bccc","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":145,"end":144}}}},"__N_SSG":true}